      <event start="T1762-050" end="T1762-707">in pol s ble itak tri tablce </event>
      <event start="T1762-707" end="T1764-755">in itak pač ... </event>
      <event start="T1764-755" end="T389">Čist, čist na strani se itak niso čuli vmes </event>
      <event start="T389" end="T491">in je s() </event>
      <event start="T491" end="T1775-014">in je folk pač naročvou isto zadevo </event>
      <event start="T1775-014" end="T1782-889">in na koncu, ko smo bl že vsi pač dan, dan, smo dobli pač štirkrat en() en() eno stvar. </event>
      <event start="T1782-889" end="T390">In si bil sam t@k: </event>
      <event start="T390" end="T1787-082">"Pa, pa za koga pa zaka?" </event>
      <event start="T1791-166" end="T392">Ne, </event>
      <event start="T392" end="T1795-429">to, to, to je mel bratranc rojsn dan. </event>
      <event start="T1817-789" end="T1819-624">[premor] </event>
      <event start="T1819-624" end="T397">O, </event>
      <event start="T397" end="T398">luba duša, </event>
      <event start="T398" end="T1822-797">a nis mela kaj b@l pametnega za barat? </event>
      <event start="T1823-517" end="T399">Mislim, </event>
      <event start="T399" end="T400">ja, </event>
      <event start="T400" end="T401">okej, </event>
      <event start="T401" end="T402">štekam, da si v študentu </event>
      <event start="T402" end="T1830-557">pa pač da maš cv@tke n@t@r, ko pač, ja, nč ne delajo za [nerazumljivo]. </event>
      <event start="T1832-358" end="T403">Sn bil, sn bil glih, glih včera sn bil v v bivšem apartmaju </event>
      <event start="T403" end="T1839-117">in je pač ... </event>
      <event start="T1839-117" end="T1841-758">Pač vidi se, da nas treh ni. </event>
      <event start="T1841-758" end="T404">J() je pač res je grozno, </event>
      <event start="T404" end="T405">pač t@k res je zanemarjeno, </event>
      <event start="T405" end="T1848-332">umivalniki polni. </event>
      <event start="T1848-332" end="T407">Ne, </event>
      <event start="T407" end="T406">pač, je ... </event>
      <event start="T406" end="T408">No, </event>
      <event start="T408" end="T409">to je, to je res fajn, ko si enkrat na svojem, </event>
      <event start="T409" end="T1855-575">pučeš tej, ko pač se t@bi zagabi. </event>
      <event start="T1855-575" end="T410">Itak sn navajen mal sproti sam za sabo spucat </event>
      <event start="T410" end="T492">pa pač je pač čedno </event>
      <event start="T492" end="T1862-036">in je to to, pač </event>
      <event start="T1862-036" end="T1865-643">nikol ne pride do takega sranja, ko je pač tam. </event>
      <event start="T1866-644" end="T1869-575">Eem men ... </event>
      <event start="T1869-575" end="T1871-794">Najrajš pučem [premor] posodo, </event>
      <event start="T1871-794" end="T1877-591">zato ku vem, da pač jo rabim nasledn dan pa </event>
      <event start="T1877-591" end="T412">pa itak pač rad kuham </event>
      <event start="T412" end="T1881-517">in je itak pač, ni panike. </event>
      <event start="T1881-517" end="T413">Eee </event>
      <event start="T413" end="T414">najslabš verjetno, </event>
      <event start="T414" end="T415">isto ko pa že prej v študentu, </event>
      <event start="T415" end="T1889-665">pač tla umivat. </event>
      <event start="T1889-665" end="T416">Pač ti tak traja, </event>
      <event start="T416" end="T1895-454">ampak n() nedo rabi in pač ... </event>
      <event start="T1895-454" end="T1897-048">[premor] </event>
      <event start="T1897-048" end="T1899-209">se ne morš izognt. </event>
      <event start="T1903-24" end="T1907-15">[premor] </event>
      <event start="T1907-15" end="T1910-047">Posodo pač v pomivalcu. </event>
      <event start="T1912-126" end="T1913-71">J@p. </event>
      <event start="T1916-347" end="T1917-066">J@p. </event>
      <event start="T1922-407" end="T1924-703">Ej ... </event>
      <event start="T1924-703" end="T1925-715">[glas] </event>
      <event start="T1925-715" end="T1926-514">Ful pomembno. </event>
      <event start="T1927-077" end="T1928-016">Eee ... </event>
      <event start="T1928-016" end="T1929-303">A(), aja. </event>
      <event start="T1929-303" end="T1929-954">Na() </event>
      <event start="T1929-954" end="T420">na() načeloma eee, </event>
      <event start="T420" end="T421">če je res kaj t@k res ogromnega kaj gr, da se lahk pole v filter nt zatakne, </event>
      <event start="T421" end="T422">drugač pa pač n@t@r daš, </event>
      <event start="T422" end="T1942-906">itak vodo pršparaš. </event>
      <event start="T1944-174" end="T493">Pač ble so raziskave, da se ti ne splača več, </event>
      <event start="T493" end="T423">da itak pač so tenk učinkoviti, da pač n() ni več poante, da bi mogu nejprej ne vem k@k umit, </event>
      <event start="T423" end="T424">pač n@t@r daš, </event>
      <event start="T424" end="T1956-680">sam vuodo zanucuješ na dveh konc@h. </event>
      <event start="T1956-680" end="T1958-729">[premor] </event>
      <event start="T1958-729" end="T1959-696">[glas] </event>
      <event start="T1962-470" end="T1964-063">[premor] </event>
      <event start="T1964-063" end="T1965-216">Eh. </event>
      <event start="T1965-216" end="T1966-837">Pač vodo prpraviš </event>
      <event start="T1966-837" end="T425">pa metlo vzameš, </event>
      <event start="T425" end="T1970-3">rumbe si še nisem nabavu. </event>
      <event start="T1972-397" end="T427">Ej, </event>
      <event start="T427" end="T1975-904">dejansko sem razmišlu pač t@k. </event>
      <event start="T1975-904" end="T494">Mislim, </event>
      <event start="T494" end="T495">nimam, </event>
      <event start="T495" end="T428">mislim, </event>
      <event start="T428" end="T1979-07">vse je ravno, </event>
      <event start="T1979-07" end="T1981-759">t@k da nimam glih kakih eem ..., </event>
      <event start="T1981-759" end="T496">t@k ko so včasih meli, </event>
      <event start="T496" end="T497">ko maš n@t@r med med vratam, </event>
      <event start="T497" end="T498">ko maš t@sti rob, </event>
      <event start="T498" end="T1989-461">ko še zej ne vem, zakaj je bva poanta. </event>
      <event start="T1989-461" end="T429">Eee </event>
      <event start="T429" end="T430">in bi pač dejansko, bi, bi dejansko jo lahk mel </event>
      <event start="T430" end="T431">pa bi po mojem kar fajn bvo, </event>
      <event start="T431" end="T432">no, </event>
      <event start="T432" end="T1996-635">sam </event>
      <event start="T1996-635" end="T2001-764">je pa sp@t, sp@t neki keša tr@ba dt za to. </event>
      <event start="T2003-677" end="T434">Eem </event>
      <event start="T434" end="T435">pa konc dneva, </event>
      <event start="T435" end="T436">sej ne vem, </event>
      <event start="T436" end="T2008-254">a jo dejan() bi dejansko rabu al ne. </event>
      <event start="T2008-254" end="T2010-402">[premor] </event>
      <event start="T2010-402" end="T2012-023">Še vseeno pač ... </event>
      <event start="T2012-023" end="T2017-481">[premor] </event>
      <event start="T2017-481" end="T437">ni, ni glih pocen </event>
