    <tier id="TIE0" speaker="ROG-dialog-0048" category="norm" type="t" display-name="ROG-dialog-0048 [norm]">
      <event start="T1-809" end="T2">Odkar si nazaj prišla, se še nisva čula. </event>
      <event start="T2" end="T3">Tako povej mi malo, kako je bilo kaj na Japonskem, </event>
      <event start="T3" end="T7-327">no. </event>
      <event start="T24-117" end="T26-515">Kako si do Zagreba prišla? </event>
      <event start="T43-813" end="T12">Čakaj, </event>
      <event start="T12" end="T46-691">do Pragerskega pa kaj? </event>
      <event start="T46-691" end="T48-133">Vlak ali bus? </event>
      <event start="T50-642" end="T51-553">Aaa. </event>
      <event start="T69-347" end="T71-301">Klasika. </event>
      <event start="T71-301" end="T73-284">A si pozabila kaj? </event>
      <event start="T91-191" end="T28">Ali s() ali si si naredila preventivno plac zato, da lahko tam eee na() eee nakupiš </event>
      <event start="T28" end="T97-756">pa zraven prineseš? </event>
      <event start="T132-941" end="T35">Dobro, dobro. </event>
      <event start="T35" end="T36">Dosti o tem, </event>
      <event start="T36" end="T135-863">okej. </event>
      <event start="T135-863" end="T37">Kje sva ostala, </event>
      <event start="T37" end="T38">prišla si do Zagreba, </event>
      <event start="T38" end="T139-613">tam si šla na letalo? </event>
      <event start="T144-457" end="T146-302">Okej. </event>
      <event start="T147-191" end="T39">Ja, </event>
      <event start="T39" end="T148-719">okej. </event>
      <event start="T183-250" end="T186-051">Tako last minute predstavitve so itak najboljše. </event>
      <event start="T186-936" end="T50">Samo čakaj, </event>
      <event start="T50" end="T190-341">to je bilo kao v sklopu faksa ali? </event>
      <event start="T241-52" end="T59">Kako, kaj je bil pa kriterij, va() </event>
      <event start="T59" end="T247-043">saj ni vas samo osem na smeri? </event>
      <event start="T280-88" end="T282-305">Ja, </event>
      <event start="T282-305" end="T282-746">poslušam še. </event>
      <event start="T282-746" end="T283-445">Fair enough. </event>
      <event start="T284-91" end="T286-12">Mislim ... </event>
      <event start="T286-12" end="T67">Okej, </event>
      <event start="T67" end="T287-884">zdaj ze() </event>
      <event start="T287-884" end="T68">zdaj si po(), zdaj si povedala, kako si sploh to zraven prišla, </event>
      <event start="T68" end="T291-736">zdaj, zdaj pa pač ... </event>
      <event start="T291-736" end="T69">eee </event>
      <event start="T69" end="T70">nadaljuj, kje, kje s(), </event>
      <event start="T70" end="T71">čakaj, </event>
      <event start="T71" end="T72">zdaj sva ... </event>
      <event start="T72" end="T298-857">zdaj si rekla, kaj je bilo na letalu. </event>
      <event start="T300-515" end="T302-159">Ja. </event>
      <event start="T339-825" end="T340-688">Pač zakaj n() ... </event>
      <event start="T340-688" end="T81">zakaj v eno zem bi mogel biti hujši </event>
      <event start="T81" end="T344-684">oziroma zakaj več traja? </event>
      <event start="T345-325" end="T347-068">Kaj ste imeli drugo turo ali kaj? </event>
      <event start="T364-803" end="T87">Okej, </event>
      <event start="T87" end="T366-501">fair enough. </event>
      <event start="T367-19" end="T88">Eee </event>
      <event start="T88" end="T370-256">prva stvar, ko si dol pristala? </event>
      <event start="T409-126" end="T415-201">Všeč mi je, da nisi rekla, da prva stvar, ko si naredila, si začela ploskati, ko ste pristali. </event>
      <event start="T417-462" end="T418-65">A veš, kaj mislim? </event>
      <event start="T418-65" end="T419-454">[nerazumljivo] </event>
      <event start="T433-295" end="T435-15">[smeh] </event>
      <event start="T435-15" end="T437-429">Fair enough. </event>
      <event start="T467-189" end="T104">A, </event>
      <event start="T104" end="T467-826">okej. </event>
      <event start="T476-56" end="T107">Ja, </event>
      <event start="T107" end="T108">samo čakaj, </event>
      <event start="T108" end="T479-244">v japonščini to ali? </event>
      <event start="T480-481" end="T110">A, </event>
      <event start="T110" end="T481-257">okej okej. </event>
      <event start="T499-145" end="T113">Škoda, </event>
      <event start="T113" end="T501-429">mi tega nimamo. </event>
      <event start="T508-261" end="T117">Mislim, </event>
      <event start="T117" end="T449">če že daš nekaj inputa noter pač, </event>
      <event start="T449" end="T516-089">da imaš vsaj filing, da se ti je splačalo sploh karkoli narediti. </event>
      <event start="T518-708" end="T120">Kaj ste še pa pol šli izven </event>
      <event start="T120" end="T121">eee, bi rekel, </event>
      <event start="T121" end="T525-887">okvirjev od faksa pogledat? </event>
      <event start="T593-182" end="T132">Čakaj, </event>
      <event start="T132" end="T595-64">za koliko dni sploh šla? </event>
      <event start="T633-11" end="T635-217">[nerazumljivo] </event>
      <event start="T644-754" end="T138">Kenslali, </event>
      <event start="T138" end="T646-913">ljuba duša. </event>
      <event start="T650-348" end="T140">S kod si pa, </event>
      <event start="T140" end="T652-533">pizdarija. </event>
      <event start="T660-603" end="T144">Skenclali, </event>
      <event start="T144" end="T663-872">ne pa skenslati, </event>
      <event start="T663-872" end="T145">mislim, </event>
      <event start="T145" end="T665-974">skenclaš. </event>
      <event start="T665-974" end="T667-421">Daj no. </event>
      <event start="T675-419" end="T678-138">A, a, a bejži. </event>
      <event start="T678-635" end="T680-155">N() ne bi si mislil. </event>
      <event start="T681-890" end="T683-763">Od kdaj naprej pa? </event>
      <event start="T685-831" end="T686-502">Mislim, </event>
      <event start="T686-502" end="T687-356">Jesus. </event>
      <event start="T728-463" end="T162">Ja čakaj, </event>
      <event start="T162" end="T457">kaj pa pol, ko si nazaj prišla, </event>
      <event start="T457" end="T733-961">ste mogli eee za faks kako poročilo narediti? </event>
      <event start="T733-961" end="T735-72">Predstaviti ... </event>
      <event start="T736-734" end="T737-801">Ali je bilo to to? </event>
      <event start="T769-315" end="T168">O fak, </event>
      <event start="T168" end="T169">ja, </event>
      <event start="T169" end="T772-68">kje sploh začeti? </event>
      <event start="T772-68" end="T773-888">[glas] </event>
      <event start="T773-888" end="T775-605">[premor] </event>
      <event start="T775-605" end="T776-85">Eee ... </event>
      <event start="T776-85" end="T778-180">[glas] </event>
      <event start="T778-180" end="T782-635">Mmm mislim eem ... </event>
      <event start="T782-635" end="T786-495">De() decembra še nisem vedel glih, kaj bo z novim letom. </event>
      <event start="T786-495" end="T170">Eee takrat, ko bi mogel dobiti šiht, </event>
      <event start="T170" end="T793-849">so pol e() enega drugega vzeli za senior pozicijo. </event>
      <event start="T793-849" end="T797-802">Eem ... [glas] </event>
      <event start="T797-802" end="T171">Pol pa, pol pa itak pač, </event>
      <event start="T171" end="T172">ko ne veš, kaj bo čez par mesecev, si pač tako ono, </event>
      <event start="T172" end="T804-422">pač bo, kaj b() ... </event>
      <event start="T804-422" end="T173">Pol pa itak prvi dan po novem letu prid() pridem v pisarno, </event>
      <event start="T173" end="T810-423">pride ta novi, </event>
      <event start="T810-423" end="T174">pa ga šef predstavi </event>
      <event start="T174" end="T813-48">pa reče: </event>
      <event start="T813-48" end="T175">"No, </event>
      <event start="T175" end="T176">toti, toti, tole je vaš študent, </event>
      <event start="T176" end="T818-149">zaenkrat še. </event>
      <event start="T818-149" end="T821-918">Delamo na tem, da bo čim prej redno zaposlen." </event>
      <event start="T821-918" end="T823-668">[premor] </event>
      <event start="T823-668" end="T178">Eem </event>
      <event start="T178" end="T177">pol pa ja, </event>
      <event start="T177" end="T459">pol pa kar naenkrat pa pač dobiš papirje od kadro(), </event>
      <event start="T459" end="T460">mislim, kadrovski vprašalnik, </event>
      <event start="T460" end="T831-369">da izpolniš pač s kod si, </event>
      <event start="T831-369" end="T834-058">kaj si. </event>
      <event start="T834-058" end="T836-000">Izobrazba. </event>
      <event start="T836-000" end="T837-537">Mmm ... </event>
      <event start="T837-537" end="T839-414">[premor] </event>
      <event start="T839-414" end="T840-242">[glas] </event>
      <event start="T840-242" end="T461">Pol itak, pač </event>
      <event start="T461" end="T843-007">kdaj bi začel delati. </event>
      <event start="T843-007" end="T462">Pol zadaj še itak, </event>
      <event start="T462" end="T179">kako si daleč si s faksom </event>
      <event start="T179" end="T180">pa kaj ti še manjka </event>
      <event start="T180" end="T852-168">pa itak vsi upajo, da boš, pač ja zaključil vse skupaj. </event>
      <event start="T853-625" end="T181">Ah, </event>
      <event start="T181" end="T182">pol pa enkrat, </event>
      <event start="T182" end="T856-253">ja ... </event>
      <event start="T856-253" end="T183">Pol pač, itak ... </event>
      <event start="T183" end="T184">Verjetno, </event>
      <event start="T184" end="T185">mislim, </event>
      <event start="T185" end="T186">pol pa itak, kak mesec traja, prej da začneš, </event>
      <event start="T186" end="T863-83">to je pač po navadi prvi v mesecu. </event>
      <event start="T863-83" end="T463">Pol imaš pa itak, glede na to, da s() izgubiš status študenta, </event>
      <event start="T463" end="T874-044">moraš itak začeti iskati nek() neko stanovanje, nekje. </event>
      <event start="T874-044" end="T878-691">Pa glede na to, da pač ... so ceste, kakršne pač so. </event>
      <event start="T878-691" end="T188">Pa da je pol štiri ure gor p() gor pa dol, da domov prideš pa nazaj, </event>
      <event start="T188" end="T884-584">a ne. </event>
      <event start="T884-584" end="T464">Je malo brez zveze, ko ti gre cel dan, </event>
      <event start="T464" end="T888-925">če si že glih v Ljubljani. </event>
      <event start="T888-925" end="T190">Mmm </event>
      <event start="T190" end="T189">pol pač začneš iskati </event>
      <event start="T189" end="T465">pa gledati ku bumbar </event>
      <event start="T465" end="T895-130">pa ogromno stresa. </event>
      <event start="T895-130" end="T897-064">[premor] </event>
      <event start="T897-064" end="T191">Ah, </event>
      <event start="T191" end="T192">pol pa končno že najdeš kaj, da da ti ustreza glede same lokacije, </event>
      <event start="T192" end="T193">pa prideš na lokacijo, </event>
      <event start="T193" end="T194">kaj imaš v opisu, da je, da imajo parkir plac, </event>
      <event start="T194" end="T195">prideš tja, </event>
      <event start="T195" end="T196">ti reče: </event>
      <event start="T196" end="T197">"Ni n() ... </event>
      <event start="T197" end="T198">Je načeloma par(), parkir plac, </event>
      <event start="T198" end="T916-364">ampak imam jaz tako velik avto, da n(), da ne, da ga ti ne moreš kam dati." </event>
      <event start="T916-364" end="T920-408">Do tega, da pač itak rabiš začasni naslov prijaviti. </event>
      <event start="T920-408" end="T199">Ti reče: </event>
      <event start="T199" end="T200">"Joj, </event>
      <event start="T200" end="T466">imamo nekega bratranca, </event>
      <event start="T466" end="T201">tole ko ima še pol leta, ko ima neko frko." </event>
      <event start="T201" end="T202">Pa si samo tako: </event>
      <event start="T202" end="T203">"Ja, pa daj, </event>
      <event start="T203" end="T927-495">no." </event>
      <event start="T928-704" end="T929-945">Eem, </event>
