      <event start="T1626-421" end="T364">In pol nardiš v bistvu v trikotnik, </event>
      <event start="T364" end="T486">in to je najbolj značilna stvar za onigiri, </event>
      <event start="T486" end="T1633-439">to, da je v trikotniku nareto. </event>
      <event start="T1633-439" end="T1636-625">In pol dobiš še alge, </event>
      <event start="T1636-625" end="T1639-889">t@te alge, ko so po navadi tud okolo sušija. </event>
      <event start="T1639-889" end="T366">Eee </event>
      <event start="T366" end="T365">dobiš alge </event>
      <event start="T365" end="T1643-912">pa pol v bistvu zaviješ. </event>
      <event start="T1645-295" end="T367">Ja, </event>
      <event start="T367" end="T1646-492">posušene alge. </event>
      <event start="T1647-586" end="T370">Ja ja ja ja ja, </event>
      <event start="T370" end="T369">pač uni lis() listi, </event>
      <event start="T369" end="T1650-468">isto ko pač maš za suši, </event>
      <event start="T1650-468" end="T1654-053">če si že kdaj suši j() jedo. </event>
      <event start="T1658-838" end="T1660-781">A U Suši, </event>
      <event start="T1660-781" end="T1661-777">ko lahk poješ kejkr hoč()? </event>
      <event start="T1662-957" end="T487">In, </event>
      <event start="T487" end="T1664-238">k@k ti je bvo? </event>
      <event start="T1670-354" end="T1671-99">Kdaj si, </event>
      <event start="T1671-99" end="T374">kdaj si pa bil? </event>
      <event start="T374" end="T1674-864">Zarad tega ker mi smo tud bli ... </event>
      <event start="T1674-864" end="T1675-727">mislim ... </event>
      <event start="T1675-727" end="T1677-103">T@ti pond@lk? </event>
      <event start="T1678-543" end="T488">Mi smo, </event>
      <event start="T488" end="T375">kdaj smo pa mi bli? </event>
      <event start="T375" end="T376">Mi smo bli pa prej(), prejšnjo ned() ... šestega, </event>
      <event start="T376" end="T1684-874">v nedelo. </event>
      <event start="T1684-874" end="T1686-524">[smeh] </event>
      <event start="T1686-524" end="T1693-412">Z z s(), z sestro in njeno sestro in z sestrinim stricom. </event>
      <event start="T1705-745" end="T1707-182">A ste mogli kaj z()... </event>
      <event start="T1719-097" end="T1721-568">[smeh] </event>
      <event start="T1721-568" end="T1728-891">Mi smo, mi smo se isto mogli ful potrudit, da smo na koncu poje(), pojedli vse, kar smo si naročli. </event>
      <event start="T1728-891" end="T1729-852">Zard tega ker </event>
      <event start="T1729-852" end="T1730-679">ne vem, </event>
      <event start="T1730-679" end="T384">od kod so vs() vs() vsi uni krožniki pršli, </event>
      <event start="T384" end="T1738-118">ampak u, kr, zarad tega ker </event>
      <event start="T1738-118" end="T385">ne vem, </event>
      <event start="T385" end="T1740-898">neki naročiš v prvi rundi, </event>
      <event start="T1740-898" end="T1747-656">in pol ti šele po, po tem, ko si ti drugo na run(), rundo naroču, ti pridu uno, ka si naroču v prvi rundi. </event>
      <event start="T1747-656" end="T1754-708">In pol si sam zmeden, od kje je pršva t@ta rolica pa kje je pršva una rolica. </event>
      <event start="T1754-708" end="T387">Ja, </event>
      <event start="T387" end="T388">tak da mi smo meli is(), isti problem, </event>
      <event start="T388" end="T1759-248">ampak smo vse pojedli. </event>
      <event start="T1762-050" end="T1762-707">Des() ... </event>
      <event start="T1787-082" end="T1788-198">[smeh] </event>
      <event start="T1788-198" end="T391">K@k, </event>
      <event start="T391" end="T1791-166">a to ste šli z šihtom? </event>
      <event start="T1795-429" end="T393">Aaa, </event>
      <event start="T393" end="T1797-737">okej. </event>
      <event start="T1797-737" end="T394">Ej, </event>
      <event start="T394" end="T1806-333">drugač prej ko sma se tud pogovarjava o stanovanju, sn te hotva vprašat mal več o t@tem stanovanju oziroma </event>
      <event start="T1806-333" end="T395">zdej ko maš svoje stanovanje, </event>
      <event start="T395" end="T1811-515">ka ti je najboljš pucat v t@tem stanovanju </event>
      <event start="T1811-515" end="T396">oziroma ka naj() n() ka ti je najhujš pucat, </event>
      <event start="T396" end="T1815-953">lahk tud to. </event>
      <event start="T1815-953" end="T1817-789">Pa k@k to spučeš pol. </event>
      <event start="T1822-797" end="T1823-517">Ne. </event>
      <event start="T1828-898" end="T1830-557">Absolutne cvetke. </event>
      <event start="T1830-557" end="T1832-358">Upam, da čujeta to. </event>
      <event start="T1862-036" end="T1862-719">Ja. </event>
      <event start="T1865-643" end="T1866-644">Ja. </event>
      <event start="T1866-644" end="T411">No, </event>
      <event start="T411" end="T1869-575">ka ka pa najrajš pučeš? </event>
      <event start="T1899-209" end="T417">K@k pa spučeš posodo </event>
      <event start="T417" end="T1903-24">pa k@k spučeš tla? </event>
      <event start="T1910-047" end="T1912-126">Pomivalc maš? </event>
      <event start="T1913-71" end="T1915-255">Ooo. </event>
      <event start="T1915-255" end="T1916-347">[smeh] </event>
      <event start="T1917-066" end="T418">Čaki, </event>
      <event start="T418" end="T419">a preden daš v pomivalc, a prvo spereš dov </event>
      <event start="T419" end="T1922-407">al sam daš n@t@r? </event>
      <event start="T1922-407" end="T1924-703">To je ful pomembno. </event>
