      <event start="T102-146" end="T107-792">zaradi tega ker sem ful eem ... [glas] </event>
      <event start="T107-792" end="T31">eee ful velikokrat rada preveč napakiram, </event>
      <event start="T31" end="T112-98">sploh kar se tiče potovanj. </event>
      <event start="T112-98" end="T32">Eem in sem </event>
