      <event start="T1606-24" end="T1610-294">Narediš eee v bistvu sploščiš toti riž. </event>
      <event start="T1610-294" end="T1616-751">In pol vzameš eno m() malo žličko totega nadeva, ko si ga naredil. </event>
      <event start="T1616-751" end="T363">Ga daš na sredino riža </event>
      <event start="T363" end="T1623-109">in pol prvo narediš vse to tako v tako kroglico, </event>
      <event start="T1623-109" end="T1626-421">tako da mora biti nadev na sredini tote kroglice. </event>
      <event start="T1626-421" end="T364">In pol narediš v bistvu v trikotnik, </event>
      <event start="T364" end="T486">in to je najbolj značilna stvar za onigiri, </event>
      <event start="T486" end="T1633-439">to, da je v trikotniku narejeno. </event>
      <event start="T1633-439" end="T1636-625">In pol dobiš še alge, </event>
      <event start="T1636-625" end="T1639-889">tote alge, ko so po navadi tudi okoli sušija. </event>
      <event start="T1639-889" end="T366">Eee </event>
      <event start="T366" end="T365">dobiš alge </event>
      <event start="T365" end="T1643-912">pa pol v bistvu zaviješ. </event>
      <event start="T1645-295" end="T367">Ja, </event>
      <event start="T367" end="T1646-492">posušene alge. </event>
      <event start="T1647-586" end="T370">Ja ja ja ja ja, </event>
      <event start="T370" end="T369">pač oni lis() listi, </event>
      <event start="T369" end="T1650-468">isto ko pač imaš za suši, </event>
      <event start="T1650-468" end="T1654-053">če si že kdaj suši je() jedel. </event>
      <event start="T1658-838" end="T1660-781">A U Sushi, </event>
      <event start="T1660-781" end="T1661-777">ko lahko poješ kolikor hoč()? </event>
      <event start="T1662-957" end="T487">In, </event>
      <event start="T487" end="T1664-238">kako ti je bilo? </event>
      <event start="T1670-354" end="T1671-99">Kdaj si, </event>
      <event start="T1671-99" end="T374">kdaj si pa bil? </event>
      <event start="T374" end="T1674-864">Zaradi tega ker mi smo tudi bili ... </event>
      <event start="T1674-864" end="T1675-727">mislim ... </event>
      <event start="T1675-727" end="T1677-103">Toti ponedeljek? </event>
      <event start="T1678-543" end="T488">Mi smo, </event>
      <event start="T488" end="T375">kdaj smo pa mi bili? </event>
      <event start="T375" end="T376">Mi smo bili pa prej(), prejšnjo ned() ... šestega, </event>
      <event start="T376" end="T1684-874">v nedeljo. </event>
      <event start="T1684-874" end="T1686-524">[smeh] </event>
      <event start="T1686-524" end="T1693-412">Z z s(), z sestro in njeno sestro in s sestrinim stricem. </event>
      <event start="T1705-745" end="T1707-182">A ste mogli kaj z()... </event>
      <event start="T1719-097" end="T1721-568">[smeh] </event>
      <event start="T1721-568" end="T1728-891">Mi smo, mi smo se isto mogli ful potruditi, da smo na koncu poje(), pojedli vse, kar smo si naročili. </event>
      <event start="T1728-891" end="T1729-852">Zaradi tega ker </event>
      <event start="T1729-852" end="T1730-679">ne vem, </event>
      <event start="T1730-679" end="T384">od kod so vs() vs() vsi oni krožniki prišli, </event>
      <event start="T384" end="T1738-118">ampak v, kar, zaradi tega ker </event>
      <event start="T1738-118" end="T385">ne vem, </event>
      <event start="T385" end="T1740-898">nekaj naročiš v prvi rundi, </event>
      <event start="T1740-898" end="T1747-656">in pol ti šele po, po tem, ko si ti drugo na run(), rundo naročil, ti pride ono, kar si naročil v prvi rundi. </event>
      <event start="T1747-656" end="T1754-708">In pol si samo zmeden, od kje je prišla tota rolica pa kje je prišla ona rolica. </event>
      <event start="T1754-708" end="T387">Ja, </event>
      <event start="T387" end="T388">tako da mi smo imeli is(), isti problem, </event>
      <event start="T388" end="T1759-248">ampak smo vse pojedli. </event>
      <event start="T1762-050" end="T1762-707">Des() ... </event>
      <event start="T1787-082" end="T1788-198">[smeh] </event>
      <event start="T1788-198" end="T391">Kako, </event>
      <event start="T391" end="T1791-166">a to ste šli s šihtom? </event>
      <event start="T1795-429" end="T393">Aaa, </event>
      <event start="T393" end="T1797-737">okej. </event>
      <event start="T1797-737" end="T394">Ej, </event>
      <event start="T394" end="T1806-333">drugače prej ko sva se tudi pogovarjala o stanovanju, sem te hotela vprašati malo več o totem stanovanju oziroma </event>
      <event start="T1806-333" end="T395">zdaj ko imaš svoje stanovanje, </event>
      <event start="T395" end="T1811-515">kaj ti je najboljše pucati v totem stanovanju </event>
      <event start="T1811-515" end="T396">oziroma kaj naj() n() kaj ti je najhujše pucati, </event>
      <event start="T396" end="T1815-953">lahko tudi to. </event>
      <event start="T1815-953" end="T1817-789">Pa kako to spučeš pol. </event>
      <event start="T1822-797" end="T1823-517">Ne. </event>
      <event start="T1828-898" end="T1830-557">Absolutne cvetke. </event>
      <event start="T1830-557" end="T1832-358">Upam, da čujeta to. </event>
      <event start="T1862-036" end="T1862-719">Ja. </event>
      <event start="T1865-643" end="T1866-644">Ja. </event>
      <event start="T1866-644" end="T411">No, </event>
      <event start="T411" end="T1869-575">kaj kaj pa najrajši pučeš? </event>
      <event start="T1899-209" end="T417">Kako pa spučeš posodo </event>
      <event start="T417" end="T1903-24">pa kako spučeš tla? </event>
      <event start="T1910-047" end="T1912-126">Pomivalec imaš? </event>
      <event start="T1913-71" end="T1915-255">Ooo. </event>
      <event start="T1915-255" end="T1916-347">[smeh] </event>
      <event start="T1917-066" end="T418">Čakaj, </event>
      <event start="T418" end="T419">a preden daš v pomivalec, a prvo spereš dol </event>
      <event start="T419" end="T1922-407">ali samo daš noter? </event>
      <event start="T1922-407" end="T1924-703">To je ful pomembno. </event>
      <event start="T1926-514" end="T1927-077">Meni. </event>
      <event start="T1929-303" end="T1929-954">[smeh] </event>
      <event start="T1942-906" end="T1944-174">Okej. </event>
      <event start="T1958-729" end="T1959-696">Eem ... </event>
      <event start="T1959-696" end="T1961-631">[premor] </event>
      <event start="T1961-631" end="T1962-470">Kaj pa tla? </event>
      <event start="T1965-216" end="T1966-837">Poden. </event>
      <event start="T1970-3" end="T426">Roomba. </event>
      <event start="T426" end="T1972-397">A bi jo imel? </event>
      <event start="T2001-764" end="T433">Mmm. </event>
      <event start="T433" end="T2003-677">Ja. </event>
      <event start="T2023-74" end="T2025-262">Okej. </event>
      <event start="T2026-923" end="T2027-331">Jej. </event>
    </tier>
    <tier id="COLLOQ_ROG-dialog-0050" speaker="ROG-dialog-0050" category="colloq" type="a" display-name="ROG-dialog-0050 [colloq]">
      <event start="T642-524" end="T643-235">Odpovedati. </event>
      <event start="T689-979" end="T153">Mhm, </event>
      <event start="T153" end="T154">ja, </event>
      <event start="T154" end="T155">to lahko odrežem, </event>
      <event start="T155" end="T692-549">ni problema. </event>
      <event start="T1387-433" end="T307">Ja, </event>
      <event start="T307" end="T308">ampak sej je v redu, </event>
      <event start="T308" end="T309">zej smo na triindvajstih minutah, </event>
      <event start="T309" end="T310">tak da </event>
      <event start="T310" end="T1392-358">eem </event>
      <event start="T1392-358" end="T1393-720">še ... </event>
      <event start="T1400-219" end="T312">Ne, ne, </event>
      <event start="T312" end="T1401-648">sej bo v redu. </event>
      <event start="T1408-585" end="T316">[smeh] Eee </event>
      <event start="T316" end="T317">bi blo dobro, da zdaj nadaljujemo, </event>
      <event start="T317" end="T1411-844">sam tolko, da ne nevmo rabli se ponavljat </event>
      <event start="T1411-844" end="T1413-073">oziroma pol metat ven, </event>
      <event start="T1413-073" end="T1416-241">pa ne vem, kaj še vse. </event>
      <event start="T1420-594" end="T319">Eee </event>
      <event start="T319" end="T1425-447">še enih sedem minut bi blo v redu al pa osem. </event>
      <event start="T1436-906" end="T328">Eee </event>
      <event start="T328" end="T329">ja, </event>
      <event start="T329" end="T330">to to bom prekino, </event>
      <event start="T330" end="T1441-066">ampak eem ... </event>
      <event start="T1443-229" end="T1444-078">A veš, </event>
      <event start="T1444-078" end="T331">ti ti si mela predstavitev o o poplavah, </event>
      <event start="T331" end="T1447-241">ne da? </event>
      <event start="T1447-241" end="T1450-839">A veš, kaj lahko nardiš, da se v redu zavaruješ pred poplavami? </event>
      <event start="T1453-16" end="T333">Lajk, </event>
      <event start="T333" end="T334">nekaj takega, kar je pač navodilo </event>
      <event start="T334" end="T1458-566">al pa eee kak pripravit onigiri. </event>
      <event start="T1461-218" end="T1462-892">Ju kuld du onigiri talk. [jezik] </event>
      <event start="T1467-430" end="T336">Eee </event>
      <event start="T336" end="T1468-667">lahko dam na pavzo. </event>
      <event start="T1468-667" end="T1470-405">Pa gremo ven pa spet not. </event>
      <event start="T1470-405" end="T1471-19">Okej. </event>
      <event start="T1472-253" end="T337">A, </event>
      <event start="T337" end="T338">okej, </event>
      <event start="T338" end="T1473-219">dela. </event>
      <event start="T1604-625" end="T1605-308">Ploščato? </event>
      <event start="T2025-262" end="T439">Ja, </event>
      <event start="T439" end="T2026-923">mislim, da bo to dovolj. </event>
      <event start="T2027-331" end="T440">Zaj mamo triintrideset minut, </event>
      <event start="T440" end="T2029-962">tak da. </event>
    </tier>
